      "rationale": "The finite-volume solver (v4.2.1) and the Python hemolysis post-processing module are maintained under Git version control. A regression test suite of 42 unit tests covers core arithmetic routines. All tests passed at the assessed release. Build and deployment procedures are documented in the software quality plan. No anomalies were recorded during the simulation campaign; all runs completed nominally."
