      "rationale": "Predicted RH values were compared against bench measurements at all five operating points. Mean absolute error was 0.08 and maximum absolute error was 0.13, both within the acceptance band. CFD systematically under-predicts RH by a small margin at high-flow conditions, consistent with known turbulence model behavior near the volute cutwater."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
