      "rationale": "All production simulations achieved residual reductions of five or more orders of magnitude. Mass imbalance across the pump domain was below 0.005% in every case. Convergence histories were reviewed for all 25 parametric cases (5 operating points × 5 geometric variants); all runs completed nominally with monotonic residual decay."
