      "rationale": "Pump geometry was digitized from CMM measurements of the physical device with dimensional tolerances ±0.05 mm. Blood analog viscosity and density were measured at 37 °C. Inlet velocity profiles were derived from Doppler flow measurements. A sensitivity analysis confirmed that ±5% variation in viscosity produces less than 2% change in predicted RH."
