    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six remaining factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission decision that the device hemolysis performance meets the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device across all five worst-case operating conditions.",
